01Gn 23:19 Then Abraham buried his wife, Sarah, there in Canaan, in the cave of Machpelah, near Mamre (also called Hebron).
01Gn 23:20 So the field and the cave were transferred from the Hittites to Abraham for use as a permanent burial place.
01Gn 24:1 Abraham was now a very old man, and the LORD had blessed him in every way.
