03Lv 7:11 "These are the instructions regarding the different kinds of peace offerings that may be presented to the LORD.
03Lv 7:12 If you present your peace offering as an expression of thanksgiving, the usual animal sacrifice must be accompanied by various kinds of bread made without yeast - thin cakes mixed with olive oil, wafers spread with oil, and cakes made of choice flour mixed with olive oil.
