03Lv 13:1 The LORD said to Moses and Aaron,
03Lv 13:2 "If anyone has a swelling or a rash or discolored skin that might develop into a serious skin disease��, that person must be brought to Aaron the priest or to one of his sons��. / ��Traditionally rendered leprosy. The Hebrew word used throughout this passage is used to describe various skin diseases ��Or one of his descendants
