04Nm 28:9 "On the Sabbath day, sacrifice two one-year-old male lambs with no defects. They must be accompanied by a grain offering of four quarts�� of choice flour moistened with olive oil, and a liquid offering. / ��Hebrew 2/10 of an ephah [4.4 liters]; also in 28.12, 20, 28
