04Nm 28:25 The seventh day of the festival will be another official day for holy assembly, and no ordinary work may be done on that day.
04Nm 28:26 "At the Festival of Harvest��, when you present the first of your new grain to the LORD, you must call an official day for holy assembly, and you may do no ordinary work on that day. / ��Hebrew Festival of Weeks. This was later called the Festival of Pentecost (see Acts 2.1). It is celebrated today as Shavuat (or Shabuoth)
04Nm 28:27 Present a special burnt offering on that day as a pleasing aroma to the LORD. It will consist of two young bulls, one ram, and seven one-year-old male lambs.
